--- !u!114 &2902752536302000490
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 5117482772788637760}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 0f939d5fcafb87a49902064df3aa78d0, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  attacks:
  - attack: {fileID: 1456114652092405297}
    randomChance: 3
  - attack: {fileID: 6103436427838045687}
    randomChance: 3
  - attack: {fileID: 4880498908657979838}
    randomChance: 2
  attackCooldown: 8
  spriteRenderer: {fileID: 1394846780799153891}
  _player: {fileID: 0}
  grounded: 0
  bounceOffWall: 0
  faceTowardPlayer: 0
  Dialogue:
  - "Oh great. A human. Staring at me like I\u2019m a decorative vegetable. I knew
    this night was going to be terrible."
  - "Don\u2019t just stand there. Wipe that smug expression off your face. Do you
    have any idea how long I\u2019ve been floating here?"
  - "Hours. HOURS. In the cold. With a candle jammed inside my skull. You think that\u2019s
    comfortable?"
  - "\u2026Still nothing. Wow. You\u2019re even creepier than the skeleton across
    the street."
  - "Let me guess. You\u2019re here to poke me. Or shake me. Or\u2014ugh\u2014take
    a picture for your \u201Caesthetic.\u201D"
  - If you even think about carving me more, I swear I will roll out of the sky,
    and kill you.
  - "You know what? Fine. Take whatever you want. Just stop looking at me like you\u2019re
    auditioning for a horror movie."
  - "\u2026And don\u2019t come back tomorrow. I\u2019m retiring after tonight."
  RepeatDialogue:
  - Back again to challenge the scary Jack-O-Lantern once more? you already lost
    (attempt_count) times
  - 'I see you''re back , do you want a reminder to never fight the scary Jack-O-Lantern.I
    will make your attempts: (attempt_count) turn to infinity.'
  - I'm getting board killing you can we just end this fast, like all other fights.
    You have already lost around (attempt_count) times. Lets just end this fast.
  dialogueTypingSpeed: 0.02
  DialogueImage: {fileID: 0}
  dialogueTxt: {fileID: 0}
  trueDialogueTypingSpeed: 0
  DontDoDialouge: 0
